# Phase 8.1 — Amazon Best Sellers Integration

## What Changed

Your product pipeline went from **100% synthetic** to **real Amazon products**.

### Before
```
User searches "beauty brush"
  → generateProducts() creates "Smart Beauty Brush Pro"
  → Fake name, fake price, fake orders
```

### After
```
User searches "beauty brush"
  → Amazon Best Sellers (Beauty) scraped
  → "Mighty Patch Original from Hero Cosmetics" returned
  → Real name + estimated business metrics
```

